For Running the server pleas follow the instructions : 
    
    1. open terminal in vscode 
    2. cd server (go to the server folder)
    3. enter the command: npm install + enter (install the node modoles from the package.json)
    4. enter the command: node app.js (running the server in port 8080 - localhost)
     
        - for get the data of messages that show in specific number please enter after the port number in the url : "messages/screen={screenNumber}" 
            for exmple : http://localhost:8080/messages/screen=2 
        - for get all messages enter : http://localhost:8080
